input_str: The third season of How to Get Away With Murder premiered Thursday night, and as is the case with many episodes of HTGAWM, it ended with a cliffhanger. In a flash-forward, Annalise Keating arrives at her house to find it extremely aflame and then sees a body being rolled into an ambulance as a nosy crowd watches. When she looks under the sheet to see who it is, she begins screaming and crying, so you know this is not just some random student from her new legal clinic. But who is it? Showrunner Pete Now
